name: Warung Babi Guling Bu Ardani
address: FGQ2+VX9, Jl. Raya, Ulakan, Kec. Manggis, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80864, Indonesia
review 1:
One of the best Babi Guling I ever had. Friendly staff and it’s too good
. After my first serve, I was still hungry and ordered the second plate till I was fully satisfied. Strongly recommended.
review 2:
Nasi Babi Guling is nice.
Please pay attention to the overall cleanliness.
I think they have tier pricing policy for different guests (locals, domestic, and tourist).
review 3: If you are looking for local cuisine nearest the Padang Bai, you need to considering to come here. It's pork based! Nice to try
review 4: Bu Ardani is a regular breakfast place for Alila Manggis staff, so I asked them to take me one morning. I didn't know babi guling was breakfast fare. At 9am, the place was busy. I ordered the special. One plate had babi guling pork, nice slivers of crispy skin, some rinds, deep fried belly, vegetables, and sambal. Another plate had rice and a bowl had this amazing spicy pork broth. If passing here going to Candidasa or the mountains, you have to make a stop. Wonderful service as well from the mother-daughter team.
review 5: Very good babi gulling but the skin wasnt crispy
